Fr Re Le Ri | Ld Ls Rd Rs
 0  0  0  0 |  0  0  0  0 # Stop
 1  0  0  0 |  1  0  1  0 # Forward
 0  1  0  0 |  0  1  0  1 # Reverse
 0  0  1  0 |  0  1  1  0 # Left Pivot
 0  0  0  1 |  1  0  0  1 # Right Pivot
 1  0  1  0 |  1  1  1  0 # Left Turn
 1  0  0  1 |  1  0  1  1 # Right Turn
 0  1  1  0 |  0  0  0  1 # Left Reverse Turn
 0  1  0  1 |  0  1  0  0 # Right Reverse Turn

Ld = Fr or (Ri and not Re)
Ls = Re xor Le
Rd = Fr or (Le and not Re)
Rs = Re xor Ri
